==Contents==

The following Kai Ni Remodels will be implemented somewhere around from Early Summer to Autumn.

===Light Cruiser Kai Ni Remodel===
*{{ShipLink|Yura}} Kai Ni confirmed as per hints and spoilers.[https://twitter.com/KanColle_STAFF/status/861384266411724803][http://kancolle.doorblog.jp/archives/51240941.html]
**Yura is to receive her Kai Ni Remodel in Early Summer.[https://twitter.com/KanColle_STAFF/status/861747776287154176]
===Kumano Kai Ni Remodel===
*{{ShipLink|Kumano}}'s Kai Ni Remodel has been confirmed for release soon. [https://twitter.com/KanColle_STAFF/status/870447403345731584]
**Release date is unknown as of current time.
===Kai Ni Remodels for multiple Battleships===
*Kai Ni remodel for {{ShipLink|Nagato}} has been confirmed to be released after [[Spring 2017 Event]] via June 2017 Comptiq Magazine Interview [http://kancolle.doorblog.jp/archives/51240941.html], and recent tweet [https://twitter.com/KanColle_STAFF/status/864641928763015168].
**{{ShipLink|Nagato}} Has received Kai Ni Update on [[Thread:563836|May 22nd Update]]
*Another Battleship is planned to receive a Kai Ni Remodel, but the identity of who it will be is currently unknown.

